              "id": "w1107",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:32px\">\n  <div style=\"text-align:center;padding:40px 28px;border-radius:16px;background:#F0FAFA\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:52px;font-weight:900;color:#5BBCBC;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:10px\">12+</span>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:8px\">年防水工程經驗</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7\">2012 年創立，深耕香港防水市場，累積豐富實戰經驗</p>\n  </div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:40px 28px;border-radius:16px;background:#F0FAFA\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:52px;font-weight:900;color:#5BBCBC;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:10px\">10,000+</span>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:8px\">宗成功工程</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7\">橫跨住宅、商業、工廠，每宗工程均有完整記錄</p>\n  </div><div style=\"text-align:center;padding:40px 28px;border-radius:16px;background:#F0FAFA\">\n    <span style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:52px;font-weight:900;color:#5BBCBC;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:10px\">3 大</span>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:8px\">服務優勢</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.7\">先勘察後施工、報價透明、重視細節，三大承諾貫穿每個工程</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
