            {
              "id": "w1120",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px\">\n  <div style=\"border:2px solid #E8EDED;border-radius:16px;padding:32px 28px\">\n    <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:#EEF9F9;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#5BBCBC\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"/><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y2=\"16.65\"/></svg>\n    </div>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:10px\">先勘察後施工</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.75\">利用紅外線熱像儀、微波掃描等儀器精確定位滲漏源頭，確保對症下藥，避免「做完又翻漏」。</p>\n  </div><div style=\"border:2px solid #E8EDED;border-radius:16px;padding:32px 28px\">\n    <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:#EEF9F9;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#5BBCBC\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z\"/><polyline points=\"14 2 14 8 20 8\"/></svg>\n    </div>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:10px\">透明報價無隱費</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.75\">報價書列明工程範圍、施工工序、所用材料及費用，工程開始後不會突然追加收費。</p>\n  </div><div style=\"border:2px solid #E8EDED;border-radius:16px;padding:32px 28px\">\n    <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:#EEF9F9;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#5BBCBC\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path d=\"M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z\"/></svg>\n    </div>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:800;color:#1A1A1A;margin-bottom:10px\">年期保養保障</h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans TC',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:1.75\">工程完成後提供年期保養，期間如有問題可聯絡我們跟進，確保防水效果持久穩定。</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
